Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved Vieira Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city where Sensei conducted, Prague...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The performance in Dvorak Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year I really wanted to go to see it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a famous pianist for a father,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,raised in a family of musicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I was small I have attended stages all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vienna...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Berlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prague...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the majestic Orchestras of Europe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then, the conducting of Sebastiano Vieira
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon I became engrossed in music...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my father's reputation I slipped into the Concert Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, tamagochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when Vieira-Sensei began to grow fond of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a small child but even so he taught me various things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,scatologist\N(a person having an interest in poops)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when my mother divorced my father and I had to go home to Japan with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equally terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look, look! It's Chiaki-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, he's heading here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A- ah, that fourth-year Chiaki-senpai? I\Ndon't know why but he's really putting on airs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That "Nani-sama", "Ore-sama", "Chiaki-sama"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:05:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give Chiaki-Sama trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your manners, okay?\NYour manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So impressive ~ even for Eto Sensei,\Nwho teaches only the super talented in\Nthe Piano Division, he's the most favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really?\N- I'm so envious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh! Let's practice our band!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Mine, shall we practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What "Chiaki" huh?\NJust a ray from his father's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is Chiaki-senpai going to have a lesson?\NMaki-chan, let's go take a little look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that Reina,\NLet's have lunch, lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought special limited depachika lunch-box\Nwith 20 kinds of dishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NODAMEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scholar to Germany decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is such a ham-looking guy\Ngoing to study abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I......
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing in such a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT ARE YOU DOING HUH?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get excited by yourself\Nthen give it up by yourself too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to do it or not, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After selecting you for the Maradona Piano\NCompetition in December,\Ndo you intend to smear my face with mud?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this your last competition\Nin the university?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The piece is by Beethoven whom you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Score?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does a piano student like you\Nhave score sheets for Conductors?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hahaha... even so carefully\Nputting checks on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...do you want to be a Conductor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THAT'S NO JOKE!\NYOU DON'T EVEN PLAY THE PIANO RIGHT... STUPID...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STOP IT, JIJI! Shouting and yelling like\Na loan-shark demanding borrowed money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What elite specialist "Eto-Juku"? Repeating\Nforte! forte! confuoco! like some dumb people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All your students play the piano\Nthe same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you admit my talent,\Ndon't teach redundant things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I say more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't come to\Nmy lesson anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask another student to appear\Nin the competition
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mistake in judging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a Conductor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beethoven, Piano Sonata, "Pathetique"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,playing it extremely messily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is truly pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although messy,\Nit was not making a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is playing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you got dropped\Nby Eto-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and apologize to Eto Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Although that Sensei is strict, he's the\Nmost talented and famous teacher in our Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After graduation Shinichi, you intend to\Ngo to Graduate School, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when you got a chance from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's OK...about Graduate School
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to be a pianist anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should have gone to\Nthe Conductor Division from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I suddenly went to the Conductor Division,\Nin reality it doesn't necessarily\Nmean that I'll get a chance to conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I get to study conducting properly on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, my teacher could only be\NVieira-Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be unnecessarily\Nindebted to other people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should quickly just study abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid, aren't you?\NTo be so scared of planes\Nthat you can't get into one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just having the experience of a rough\Nemergency landing ONCE, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, because of the trauma drowning\Nin the sea, you can't go by ship either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never experienced it.\NWhat do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... maybe I should quit music...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I become a professional\Nconductor in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use if I can't\Nperform in Europe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe I should just ask to be an employee\Nin your family's company, Tagaya Music Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go home... today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not in such relationship anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you are,\Nit'll just be the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,poop poop poop cat's ...pooooooop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's-his-name"- senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the sound of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a quiet place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next it's a piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece... is the one I heard at\Nthat time, Beethoven's Piano Sonata
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piano Sonata, which echoed\Nbeautifully within the garbage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capriccioso Cantabile...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Willfully, wistfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as if being sung...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember last night? Heeee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? This is my mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My......
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...neighbor's room!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... what's that female?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai, hee...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A student from my school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! My belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I DON'T REMEMBER!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heehee...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame Cantabile - Lesson 1\NSync: NIZ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left it in my place this morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that I survived in\Nthat room full of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not mine... that belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Senpai's!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed to be\Nconstricted that's why I took it off, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mistook me for a different person\NThat's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no it is really no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the smell is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson Instructor Change\NPiano Division: 4th Year Chiaki Shinichi\NInstructor: Eto Kozo  --> Tanioka Hajime
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanioka Hajime?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3203\NTanioka Hajime
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suits well for cheering, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes the last part was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seemed to have entered the wrong room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for you, Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaa, seeing you in person,\Nthe aura's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I won't let you call\Nme Ochisen, haha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochisen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochikobore Specialist Teacher.\NWhat a terrible talk, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not talk while standing.\NPlease sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ore...... an underachiever??\N(Ore = I)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what about this belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Momogaoka Music Academy's "A-Oke" is an elite\NOrchestra consisting of the most talented students\N(A-Oke = A-Orchestra)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our concert this year will have Miki Kiyora\Nas Concert Mistress.\NIn the future, other gifted students will join too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to our performance next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're almost getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However from now on\Nis the crucial moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm expecting the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rijichou (Board Chairman),\Nallow me to introduce...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Classic Life monthly magazine's\NKawano-san
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... somehow there's something lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? Sorry! It's not Classic Life,\Nbut our A-Oke
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, they always do the same thing,\Ndon't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think they've achieved a high level...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes that's true
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After they graduate they will\Nmost likely be succesful
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, not letting their talent fades away\Nwithout any chance to grow is essentially our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I can do something for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two pianos?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, won't you try it? Third year Noda\NMegumi-kun and you, Chiaki-kun,\Nwill have a two-piano lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that you two know\Neach other. it's just right for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. Why do I have to\Ntake lessons with such a female?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame chose this one to play! Heehee...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do it the usual way\Nonly with Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A piano duet played by two people is very interesting.\NMoreover Noda-kun's piano is very good...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how good she is, it's impossible to adjust\Nto such a person who plays so messily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's not impossible if it's you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you play the piano the best\Nin this Music Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, well what can I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as advising your Kohai?\N(Kohai = younger fellow student/colleague)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mozart\NSonata for two pianos
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeek, I don't know this piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never played this before either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I think it'll be tough to adjust\Nto each other with this fast piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, be patient and keep practising it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Let's look at it once,\Nthen get it done and over with,\NGarbage Female!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Nodame please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For tempo it's OK to be slow,\Nabout this speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a mistake in just two sections!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she play so sloppily?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not looking at the score!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was reading correctly....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's correct with those tat-tat-tat\Nand pat-pat-pat? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just somehow doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun's ear is very good, she often\Nlearns by listening, she's not accustomed\Nto play while looking at the scores...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why she plays so messily
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover she hates to practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, relax and do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For this sort of lesson,\Nthree days is more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we have for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Saiko!\NDumping me for such a ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT'S THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.58,0:24:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.45,0:24:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do people normally open the door\Nin one swing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.25,0:24:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The belt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.13,0:24:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, if you came for the belt,\Nhere it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.03,0:24:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.58,0:24:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take out all your cleaning tools!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.20,0:24:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.67,0:24:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If vacum cleaner, it's always\Nkept outside in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.84,0:24:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.00,0:24:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on top of the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.18,0:25:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.62,0:25:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.81,0:25:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks!\NIt stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.67,0:25:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with this mountain of garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.12,0:25:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will throw them all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.85,0:25:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.05,0:25:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This box contains many necessary stuff\Nlike school stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.97,0:25:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.98,0:25:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The box contains sweets sent from\Nmy hometown, I can't survive without these...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.24,0:25:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo! Not that! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.54,0:25:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my treasure... yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.35,0:25:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.27,0:25:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.30,0:25:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.09,0:25:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably cream stew...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.14,0:25:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is cream stew black? And coiling like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.68,0:25:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it was there\Nsince a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.93,0:26:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're these fish roes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.16,0:26:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.47,0:26:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!... What's this... this mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.74,0:26:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.60,0:26:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaaa! Brassierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.14,0:26:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiyaaa!! Panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.27,0:26:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.26,0:26:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.61,0:26:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With no garbage, the sound\Nof piano is completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.68,0:26:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.31,0:26:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah Senpai, as a sign of my gratitude,\NI cooked something for you! Please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.89,0:26:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.89,0:26:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.89,0:26:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ass Fortunetelling"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.85,0:27:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.64,0:27:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salted horse mackerel with mayonnaise sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.87,0:27:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asking you what's this BLACK thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.12,0:27:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horse mackerel
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.04,0:27:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's charcoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.82,0:27:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.97,0:27:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you cook by yourself, only say it\Nafter you can cook something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.47,0:27:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaaa! Wonderful! Wonderful!\NWhat's this called?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.56,0:27:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meringue a la penne con i broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.18,0:27:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy! Wonderful!\NYummier than what my Mom cooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.79,0:27:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.51,0:27:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.93,0:27:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame is sooo impressed! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.39,0:27:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I'll cook yummier stuff for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.70,0:27:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.51,0:27:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rijichou, it's almost time already.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.71,0:27:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to meet someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.74,0:27:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always loose when it comes to keeping time...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.04,0:27:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chinese Food "Uraken"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.22,0:27:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, why didn't you wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.45,0:28:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I told you that if I don't pass today's\Nafternoon class I will have to stay the same year?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.23,0:28:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid!\NDoing this everyday at your age!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.55,0:28:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully at the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.55,0:28:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still lunch break!\NYou, silly boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.39,0:28:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just five minutes to school from here.\NI wanted to let you sleep until just\Nten minutes before the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.44,0:28:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.20,0:28:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.87,0:28:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never eaten such delicious\Nboiled vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.28,0:28:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.60,0:28:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next, hey, the-man-with-a-good-taste! Ojisan, order\Nwhatever you like! Noodles, curry, oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.57,0:28:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever dish my father cooks,\Nit's very delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.08,0:28:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Oden?\N(Oden = boiled fish cakes and radish etc\Nin hot soup)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.38,0:28:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially boiled konbu with katsuo\N(boiled seaweed shining with tuna)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.85,0:28:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kotobu shining with katsura\N(back of head shining with wig)\N(he is making a pun)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.25,0:28:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... so you're not Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.69,0:28:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... a Music Academy student?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.42,0:28:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiisan is weird. Let me tell you it's boring\Nto tour inside a Music Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.46,0:28:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Oke, "Eto Juku", those are trivial!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.71,0:29:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generally viewing us based only on\Nclassical music, how stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.21,0:29:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the whole world is rich with music...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.46,0:29:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,jazz, pop, and then rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.32,0:29:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,520... 526...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.52,0:29:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.23,0:29:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such... such a small practice room...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.44,0:29:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.69,0:29:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.41,0:29:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.68,0:29:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.90,0:29:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.44,0:29:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always at the same place. It's\Nbecause you always take part-timer jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.99,0:30:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.44,0:30:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, music is Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.08,0:30:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.36,0:30:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be one of my fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.52,0:30:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.51,0:30:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi-chan? Could it be that\NMasumi-chan was also peeped at?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.05,0:30:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No I'm just claustrophobic...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.86,0:30:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... but please be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.15,0:30:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that there is a strange\Nold man walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.07,0:30:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's a stalker of Moe-san and Kaori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.06,0:30:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that he's stalking\NChiaki-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.91,0:30:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. That's Masumi-chan, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.53,0:30:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.09,0:31:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just... I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.13,0:31:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looking at Chiaki-Sama everyday\Nfor these four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.28,0:31:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sonata For Two Pianos"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.39,0:31:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cheerful and suitable for a salon piece\Nwas composed in the latter part of the 18th century\Nto be performed with an acquiantance's gifted daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.38,0:31:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only piano duet piece that Mozart\Ncomposed in his whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.15,0:31:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanioka-sensei sure is mean
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.54,0:31:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other pieces that are easier to do,\Nwhy chose this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.56,0:31:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be tough to do it in three days as I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.59,0:32:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.59,0:32:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, Noda-kun is not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.76,0:32:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hardly arrives on time, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.96,0:32:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.24,0:32:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a formal class
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.93,0:32:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sometimes I'm also late...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.33,0:32:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go out for a bit to drink some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.41,0:32:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.29,0:32:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...I'm Conductor Division's...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.02,0:32:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.81,0:32:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally. Hayakawa-kun is famous!\NAnd I'm the secondly famous\NOokuchi Mamoru from Conducting Division...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.90,0:32:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my destination I'm thinking of\Ntaking lectures at Gerhalm
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.07,0:32:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.01,0:32:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gerhalm?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.21,0:32:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that Seminar, Sebastiano Vieira\Nwill come to teach special courses, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.83,0:32:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in any case I'll also go in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.49,0:33:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Saiko-chan that\NChiaki-kun and Vieira-sensei know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.98,0:33:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I meet him, I will tell him any message from you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.71,0:33:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai is so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.09,0:33:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.\NLet's begin by ourselves first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.25,0:33:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that Seminar Sebastiano Vieira\Nwill come to teach special courses, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.93,0:33:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I meet him I will tell him any message from you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.75,0:33:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate losers
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.93,0:33:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you are,\Nit'll be just the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.91,0:34:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.61,0:34:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I have for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.27,0:34:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.35,0:34:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the earlier fantasy girl!\NGood evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.80,0:34:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.65,0:34:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I tell you the road where taxis usually pass?\N(wrong japanese, should be "could you tell me")
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.45,0:34:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A road where taxis usually pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.16,0:34:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh go there, turn to the left,\Nturn to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.61,0:34:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a gentle nice girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.61,0:34:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.27,0:34:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.30,0:34:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bitte, could you show me the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.10,0:34:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bitte??\N("please" in German)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.10,0:34:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.73,0:34:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.11,0:34:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no, it is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.17,0:34:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told not to follow any stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.06,0:35:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nein?? I am a moral tourist from Germany\N(nein = "no" in German)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.28,0:35:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Milch Holstein\N(Milk Cow in German)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.82,0:35:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan changed a lot,\NI don't understand anything here
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.47,0:35:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an old man and alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.70,0:35:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel very lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.51,0:35:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh you're all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.48,0:35:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.33,0:35:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat together with Nodame
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.98,0:35:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.99,0:35:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah I'm worried about Chiaki-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.05,0:35:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go and grab a meal with Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.50,0:35:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chaaaaaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.58,0:35:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready! It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.45,0:35:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.84,0:35:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is smelling bouquet garni.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.05,0:35:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is French home-cooking, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.95,0:35:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat before they get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.43,0:35:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow there is wine here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.32,0:35:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai you sit here too!\NLet's eat together!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.57,0:35:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "sit here sit here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.90,0:35:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose place do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.29,0:35:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who's this Jiisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.64,0:35:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two robbers? You've got to be robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.41,0:35:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink that wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.56,0:36:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, this is not your apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.36,0:36:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame's apartment is...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.46,0:36:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IS NEXT DOOR!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.01,0:36:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this suspicious-looking Jiisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.88,0:36:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not suspicious-looking,\Nhe's my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.21,0:36:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him on the street earlier...\NHis name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.74,0:36:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just met him on the steet?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.26,0:36:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, just because of that he's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.63,0:36:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh his name is Milch...\NMilch Holstein-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.99,0:36:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milch Holstein...?\NMilk Cow?\NObviously that's a fake-name!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hao, do you understand German?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.37,0:36:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai, this is Chiaki-senpai.\NHe is very bright and very good at piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.93,0:36:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hao, I want to listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.33,0:36:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hao, that's a very nice piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.24,0:36:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whooo, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.71,0:36:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, you sure he's not a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.50,0:36:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, do you personally know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.65,0:36:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my teacher in conducting,\Ndon't you dare touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.04,0:36:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conductor? You want to be a Conductor?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.75,0:36:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any problem to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.05,0:36:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.39,0:37:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We seem to be bothering Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.83,0:37:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hotel I'm staying\Nthere's a good sushi restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.89,0:37:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaa... sushi restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.51,0:37:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.07,0:37:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.87,0:37:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this old man is no more than\Na dirty old man, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.60,0:37:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.12,0:37:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Specially for today,\Ninside my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.89,0:37:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.23,0:37:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will advise you on your practice
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.62,0:37:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.28,0:37:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, I will teach you\Neven more enjoyable thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.59,0:37:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside a room with a beautiful sunrise scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.00,0:37:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a fluffy-fluffy bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.86,0:37:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fluffy-fluffy pillow...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.10,0:37:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful room? Fluffy-fluffy pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.98,0:37:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun! Gochisosama! Hahao!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.03,0:37:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.96,0:37:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! I also have it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.07,0:37:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fluffy-fluffy bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.27,0:37:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Senpai's bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.89,0:38:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.76,0:38:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.38,0:38:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ude-makura\N(arm-pillow, his own arm)
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.57,0:38:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.65,0:38:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Nodame-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.91,0:38:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, let go off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.33,0:38:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's that, Ojisan, have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.11,0:38:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I give you this coupon.\NIt was in the post box.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.38,0:38:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.49,0:38:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Douzo, Shinichi-san...\NIyaaaaaaaaaaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.62,0:38:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that "iyaaaaaa" you're saying!\NThis is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.66,0:38:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.81,0:38:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To bring such an immoral old man in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.96,0:38:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too go home! You flea!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.36,0:38:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!\NLiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.01,0:38:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay Okay I will practice!\NLet's practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.14,0:38:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame will practice properly, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.96,0:38:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I will do it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.31,0:38:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.78,0:38:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.70,0:38:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today you didn't come to our practice either
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.51,0:39:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.01,0:39:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheets for Conductors?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.94,0:39:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's full of checks!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.75,0:39:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was true earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.86,0:39:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Senpai wants to be a conductor...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.03,0:39:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame also wishes to see Senpai conducting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.45,0:39:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.71,0:39:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the use of studying this... it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.03,0:39:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However hard I study...\Nhowever good I become at piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.63,0:39:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the end, I'm defeated even by that Ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.94,0:39:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, even until now
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.64,0:39:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only watch orchestras from afar...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to teach you.\NYou don't want to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.57,0:39:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we leave it at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.61,0:39:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the start it's a meaningless assignment
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.80,0:40:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to force ourselves to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.17,0:40:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.93,0:40:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the one telling Tanioka-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.68,0:40:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say that I'm unable to guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.83,0:41:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is about cleaning-up,\Nthere's still enough time...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.58,0:41:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about cleaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.87,0:41:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooooo......
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.50,0:41:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that 'Noooo' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.92,0:41:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears ached hearing such terrible piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.65,0:42:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.43,0:42:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been a few days, why it's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.09,0:42:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.11,0:42:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play the notes well yet,\Nbut I'll do my best to memorize them,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.41,0:42:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please wait for a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.08,0:42:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The promise was three days
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.70,0:42:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will play it well,\Nand you listen while looking at the sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.22,0:42:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you can't learn by looking at the scores,\Nthen listen and learn with your prided ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.05,0:42:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.21,0:42:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's piano is so accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.60,0:42:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really according to the scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.16,0:42:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too sloppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.58,0:42:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're playing with me\NI want you to do it accurately, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.57,0:43:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's where we change places!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.95,0:43:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Softer!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.38,0:43:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your left hand is too loud!\NHow many times I must tell you that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.27,0:43:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play smoothly there!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.17,0:43:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to my playing carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.72,0:43:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that face!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.15,0:43:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.28,0:43:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not in harmony at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.63,0:43:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it your own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.15,0:43:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I feel so upset
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.76,0:43:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though I know I was not saying\Nanything wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.72,0:43:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get excited by yourself\Nthen give it up by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.44,0:43:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to do it or not, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.13,0:43:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, I'm no different from Harisen\N(Harisen = Eto Sensei)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.01,0:44:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The type of teaching that I abhor,\Nis what I'm exactly doing to her
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.72,0:44:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.49,0:44:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally I did it to the last part\Nwithout stumbling...\NWas there something strange again?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.81,0:44:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.01,0:44:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.54,0:44:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.68,0:44:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.96,0:44:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your head...it stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.14,0:44:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEH!? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.63,0:44:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've washed it three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.74,0:44:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.79,0:44:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, bath is every other day,\Nshampoo is once every three days... heee
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.84,0:44:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might look dirty, but in fact\NI like to keep clean, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.32,0:45:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "I might look dirty"?\NThat's three days without shampooing!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.87,0:45:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopppppppp itttt!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.24,0:45:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of upbringing did you receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.45,0:45:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopppp itt!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.62,0:45:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.41,0:45:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaa... I feel good!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.83,0:45:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame feels like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.00,0:45:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.91,0:45:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog? What kind of dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.01,0:45:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,golden retriever? chihuahua? maybe shibaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.38,0:45:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.61,0:45:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She resembles Vieira-Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.01,0:45:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.24,0:46:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.53,0:46:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with this?\NIf it's impossible,you may have a few more days
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.85,0:46:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to do it in three days
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.56,0:46:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Noda-kun is looking at the score!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.02,0:46:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.21,0:46:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For today, you may play it as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.49,0:46:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.22,0:47:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just called me Nodame...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.71,0:47:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...\Nshe CERTAINLY has something special...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.64,0:47:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who ia able to adjust to her piano is\Njust someone like Ore-Sama!\N(Ore-Sama = haughty way of saying I)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.85,0:47:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now it's a perfect unison...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.62,0:47:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.58,0:47:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first piano is most of the time\Nlightly playing the lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.82,0:47:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It showed up now... that mouth...\Nshe's starting to be out of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.23,0:47:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I told her that she\Ncould do it freely,\Nshe really becomes herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.38,0:47:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll show I can keep up with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.17,0:48:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know her habit
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.56,0:48:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! She skipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.50,0:48:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And bounced!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.67,0:48:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact I was constantly bothered\Nby her piano
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.00,0:48:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, Vieira-Sensei once said
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.97,0:49:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then I've been dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.15,0:49:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which I gave up until last night
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.69,0:49:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, for sure\Nmy body feels a little shiver
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.30,0:49:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.56,0:49:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it good Chiaki-kun, it seems\Nthat you managed to go over the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.12,0:49:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.09,0:50:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was never about teaching a kouhai,\Nbut it was a lesson for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.40,0:50:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People said Mozart, the genius, composed\Nthis one-and-only piano duet piece\Nfor the sake of playing it with a gifted pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.44,0:50:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, perhaps by playing along with her he\Nhimself wanted to recall how to purely enjoy music
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.75,0:50:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Raccoon Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.99,0:50:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at Senpai's back, I feel my heart thumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.16,0:50:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...as I thought...\N"falling in love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.71,0:50:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's wrong! It's definitely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.60,0:50:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my heart feels so tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.74,0:50:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today it just happened that the music went well,\Nbut normally such playing is not allowed, ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.69,0:50:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't play by the score\Nthen it's out of the question to\Ntake part in competitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.15,0:50:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame in a competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.14,0:50:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.10,0:50:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on!\NNodame certainly won't join in any competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.65,0:51:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you enter Music Academy,\Nand practise everyday?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.24,0:51:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Nodame wants to be\Na kindergarten teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.81,0:51:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.35,0:51:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.89,0:51:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved Vieira-Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.25,0:51:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems that in Japan\Nthere is an amazing person as well
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.92,0:51:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more things I can still do here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.50,0:51:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Application to change divisions
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.69,0:52:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, big news! They said that Stresemann\Nis coming to our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.69,0:52:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that Stresemann is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.43,0:52:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stresemann? That world-class Conductor\Nwho's comparable to Sebastiano Vieira?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.76,0:52:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll come to our A-Oke too?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.27,0:52:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A famous person is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.56,0:52:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, though for us in Piano Division,\NThe Orchestra Divison is none of our business
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.51,0:52:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's arrived in the Teachers' Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.67,0:52:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stresemann! Stresemann!\NWorld-famous Conductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.96,0:52:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really silly people, what's so great\Nabout Stresemann coming to Conducting Division?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.86,0:53:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible, just when I am about to\Nsubmit my request to move to the Conducting Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.49,0:53:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow... the eyes are a bit different...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.97,0:53:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.00,0:53:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? where? Where? where?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.70,0:53:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gehhh! That Ojiisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.93,0:53:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you want to form a new student orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.86,0:53:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Using the students I chose,\NMY Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.77,0:53:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Sensei will be looking for those\Nin the Conductor Division and the A-Oke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.30,0:53:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.37,0:54:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well of course! However, I want more students\Nto have a chance in taking my lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.03,0:54:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little bit different?\NHe looks TOTALLY different!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.89,0:54:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please gather the students who are in\Nthese photos here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.10,0:54:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhhh... my mistake, my mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.69,0:54:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my treasure photos,\Nwhich I bought in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.26,0:54:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the real stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.11,0:54:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maestro... are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.68,0:54:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this one... is from the Piano Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.25,0:54:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.06,0:54:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way or that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.95,0:54:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't change divisions!
